## Repository Layout

```
docs/                    ← ALL chapter content lives here (Docusaurus)
  part-i-foundations/    ← Ch 1–6 (Ch 6 = Hermes platform design before AWS)
  part-ii-aws/           ← Ch 7–15
  part-iii-containers/   ← Ch 16–18
  part-iv-kubernetes/    ← Ch 19–27
  part-v-infrastructure/ ← Ch 28–32
  part-vi-ai/            ← Ch 33–37 (Hermes, models, agents)
  part-vii-hermes/       ← Ch 38–43 (Hermes agent platform)
  appendices/
sidebars.ts              ← Sidebar navigation (keep in sync with SUMMARY)
docusaurus.config.ts     ← Site config
labs/                    ← Lab assets and worksheets (not published as chapters)
diagrams/                ← Reusable diagram sources
```

**Do not** create or edit under a legacy `chapters/` path — it was removed during the Docusaurus migration.

